# AI Assistant Instructions - Threat Modeling Framework

**Project:** LLM Instruction Sets and Methodology for Threat Modeling  
**Purpose:** Target-agnostic guidance for AI assistants conducting security research  
**Scope:** All security research targets in the `targets/` directory

---

## 🚀 Quick Start

**New to this framework?**
- **FIRST:** Read `.ai-instructions/core/entry-point.md` - Complete framework overview
- **THEN:** Read `.ai-instructions/skills/README.md` - Skills framework and getting started guide
- **NEXT:** Read `.ai-instructions/skills/WORKFLOW-GUIDE.md` - Stage-by-stage execution patterns

**Key Resources (Load as Needed):**
- **Operational Modes:** `.ai-instructions/modes/collaborative-mode.md` or `.ai-instructions/modes/automatic-mode.md`
- **Quality Assurance:** `.ai-instructions/quality-assurance/core-principles.md` (start here)
- **Terminology:** `.ai-instructions/skills/shared/core-terms.md` (core concepts for all stages)
- **Confidence Levels:** `.ai-instructions/skills/shared/confidence-calibration.md`

