## Repository Structure

**Multi-Target Security Research Environment:**
- **`targets/`** - Security research targets with individual directories
- **`.ai-instructions/core/`** - Central framework documentation and entry point
- **`.ai-instructions/skills/`** - Modular skills framework (PRIMARY approach)
- **`.ai-instructions/quality-assurance/`** - Quality validation framework
- **`.ai-instructions/modes/`** - Operational mode definitions (Collaborative/Automatic)

**Complete structure:** See `.ai-instructions/core/entry-point.md`

