## 6-Stage Workflow - File Loading Pattern

**Complete details:** `.ai-instructions/skills/WORKFLOW-GUIDE.md`

| Stage | Primary Guide | Validation | Key Frameworks |
|-------|---------------|------------|----------------|
| **1. System Understanding** | `documentation-specialist/stage-1-guide.md` | `quality-critic/stage-validation-guide.md` (S1) | `shared/core-terms.md` |
| **2. Data Flow Analysis** | `documentation-specialist/stage-2-guide.md` | `quality-critic/stage-validation-guide.md` (S2) | `shared/confidence-calibration.md` |
| **3. Threat Identification** | `threat-modeler/stage-3-threat-identification.md` | `quality-critic/stage-validation-guide.md` (S3) | `frameworks/quick-reference.md` (or `detailed/` versions) |
| **4. Risk Assessment** | `threat-modeler/stage-4-risk-assessment.md` | `quality-critic/stage-validation-guide.md` (S4) | `shared/confidence-calibration.md` |
| **5. Mitigation Strategy** | `threat-modeler/stage-5-mitigation-strategy.md` | `quality-critic/stage-validation-guide.md` (S5) | `shared/output-file-requirements.md` |
| **6. Final Reporting** | `threat-modeler/stage-6-final-reporting.md` | `quality-critic/stage-validation-guide.md` (S6) | `documentation-specialist/stage-6-guide.md` |

**All paths relative to:** `.ai-instructions/skills/`

